{"id":23491,"date":"2023-02-01T14:00:30","date_gmt":"2023-02-01T13:00:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/?page_id=23491"},"modified":"2024-05-29T16:22:36","modified_gmt":"2024-05-29T14:22:36","slug":"apu-i-malmo","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/karriar\/studentmojligheter\/apu-i-malmo\/","title":{"rendered":"APU i Malm\u00f6"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"preamble\">\u00c4r du nyfiken p\u00e5 hur det \u00e4r att arbeta p\u00e5 en internationell aff\u00e4rsjuridisk byr\u00e5? Arbetsplatsknutet utredningsarbete (APU) \u00e4r en f\u00f6rdjupningskurs som g\u00e5r att l\u00e4sa p\u00e5 juristprogrammet vid Lunds universitet. Mannheimer Swartling erbjuder praktikplatser inom ramen f\u00f6r APU om b\u00e5de 15 hp och 30 hp p\u00e5 v\u00e5rt kontor i Malm\u00f6.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-23492 alignnone\" src=\"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/02\/03-1395-1200x800.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/02\/03-1395-1200x800.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/02\/03-1395-2000x1333.jpg 2000w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/02\/03-1395-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/02\/03-1395-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/02\/03-1395-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2023\/02\/03-1395-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Under praktiken f\u00e5r du bland annat sj\u00e4lv utf\u00f6ra juridiska arbetsuppgifter och delta i l\u00e4rorika utbildningar som under dessa veckor h\u00e5lls inom ramen f\u00f6r v\u00e5rt utbildningsprogram. Du f\u00e5r \u00e4ven en fadder som introducerar dig till byr\u00e5n och st\u00f6ttar dig i arbetet samt v\u00e4rdefull och utvecklande erfarenhet under v\u00e4gledning av v\u00e5ra associates och partners.<\/p>\n<p>Praktiken ger dig en n\u00e4rmare inblick i rollen som aff\u00e4rsjurist hos oss och m\u00f6jlighet att bekanta dig med hur v\u00e5r f\u00f6retagskultur avspeglar sig i v\u00e5rt arbetss\u00e4tt och hos v\u00e5ra medarbetare.<\/p>\n<p>V\u00e4lkommen med din <a href=\"mailto:kristina.ekelow@msa.se\">ans\u00f6kan<\/a>!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u00c4r du nyfiken p\u00e5 hur det \u00e4r att arbeta p\u00e5 en internationell aff\u00e4rsjuridisk byr\u00e5? Arbetsplatsknutet utredningsarbete (APU) \u00e4r en f\u00f6rdjupningskurs som g\u00e5r att l\u00e4sa p\u00e5\u2026<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":10,"featured_media":0,"parent":8754,"menu_order":8,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-23491","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"lang":"sv","translations":{"sv":23491},"pll_sync_post":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/23491"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/10"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=23491"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/23491\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":27492,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/23491\/revisions\/27492"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/8754"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=23491"}],"curies"